name="date-added">2023-09-15</fr:meta></fr:frontmatter><fr:mainmatter><fr:p>
  A space <fr:tex>X</fr:tex> is <fr:link
href="axt-000R.xml"
type="local"
addr="axt-000R">compact</fr:link> iff for every family <fr:tex>\{  F_i  \} _{i  \in    I}</fr:tex> of closed sets having the <fr:link
href="axt-004Y.xml"
type="local"
addr="axt-004Y">finite intersection property</fr:link>, the intersection
  <fr:tex>\bigcap _{i  \in  I} F_i</fr:tex> is nonempty.
</fr:p></fr:mainmatter><fr:backmatter><fr:contributions></fr:contributions><fr:context></fr:context><fr:related><fr:tree
